header.HomeHero
  h1.HomeHero-title Denver Startup Week
  div.HomeHero-content
    - if AnnualSchedule.post_week? && AnnualSchedule.next.present?
      div.HomeHero-date #{AnnualSchedule.next.week_start_at.try(:strftime, '%B %e')}-#{AnnualSchedule.next.week_end_at.try(:strftime, "%e, %Y")}
    - else
      div.HomeHero-date #{AnnualSchedule.current.week_start_at.try(:strftime, '%B %e')}-#{AnnualSchedule.current.week_end_at.try(:strftime, "%e, %Y")}
    p.HomeHero-description Built by the community, for the community Denver Startup Week is a celebration of everything entrepreneurial in Denver and is the largest free event of its kind. In 2020, we will host the first ever virtual Denver Startup Week to come together, celebrate a thriving entrepreneurial ecosystem in Denver and beyond, and showcase and build the cityâ€™s culture of innovation. Now is the time to get involved as we look forward to Denver Startup Week 2020!
    - if registration_open? && !registered?
      a.HomeHero-link(href="#{register_path}")
        | Register to Attend
        span.HomeHero-link-arrow = render partial: 'icons/arrow_right'
